All Classes

Class Description
BaseYarn
BaseYarn is an abstract superclass for yarn.
Customizeable
Customizeable is an interface for Objects that need a custom value counter.
Customizer
Customizer is used to customize the knitting instruction to fit the custom yarn instead of the yarn used in the instruction.
CustomYarn
CustomYarn is used as the yarn to be fitted in place of the instructional yarn.
Engine
Engine is used to run the UI, and the program at CLI.
Instruction
Instruction holds the instructional values of the knit piece.
InstructionalYarn
InstructionalYarn is used as the yarn given in the knitting instruction.
Main
This is the entry point class to run the program.
MeterageRange
MeterageRange is a class that matches YarnTypes to their meterage.
NeedleSizeRange
NeedleSizeRange is a class used for setting the standard needle size based on yarn thickness (yarn type).
Printer
Printer is a util tool for CLI output.
YarnType
YarnType is standard yarn weight based typing system.
